Package org.cytoscape.io.write

Interface CyWriterFactory

All Superinterfaces:
CyFileFilterProvider
All Known Subinterfaces:
CyNetworkViewWriterFactory, CyPropertyWriterFactory, CySessionWriterFactory, CyTableWriterFactory, PresentationWriterFactory, VizmapWriterFactory
public interface CyWriterFactory extends CyFileFilterProvider
A marker interface used to identify factories that create CyWriter instances.

Cytoscape Backwards Compatibility (SPI Interface): We expect that this interface will be implemented. Therefore to maintain backwards compatibility this interface will only be modified for major version updates.

Module: io-api

To use this in your app, include the following dependency in your POM:

<dependency>
    <groupId>org.cytoscape</groupId>
    <artifactId>io-api</artifactId>
</dependency>
